The '''plain-colored tanager''' ('''''Tangara inornata''''') is a species of [[bird]] in the family [[Thraupidae]]. It is found in [[Colombia]], [[Costa Rica]], and [[Panama]]. Its natural [[habitat]]s are subtropical or tropical moist lowland [[forest]]s and heavily degraded former forest.

